(758, 1, '2014-01-11 13:00:12', '2014-01-11 18:00:12', 'More and more data is being generated by people engaging in everyday activities. The resulting data exhaust is an amazing source of insight about human behavior. This talk will review the evolution of data technologies; explore why this shift is happening now; and discuss what is likely to change in the near future. ', 'Our Data-Driven Future', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'data-driven-future', '', '', '2014-03-04 11:50:36', '2014-03-04 16:50:36', '', 0, 'http://waq2014.lvh.me/?post_type=session&#038;p=758', 0, 'session', '', 0),
