(760, 1, '2014-01-11 13:03:30', '2014-01-11 18:03:30', 'In Canada, 69% of consumers expect to be able to use a credit card where they shop. But for many of the local businesses, accepting credit cards is too complicated and expensive. More than two thirds of small businesses in Canada don’t accept credit cards for this reason, leaving hundreds and thousands of small businesses in Canada unable to meet their customers’ expectations and without this key tool. Square started to solve this very real problem because every seller should have the tools to make selling simple. With the right tools made affordable and accessible, every seller – individual or small business – never has to miss an opportunity to participate in commerce.', 'Making Commerce Easy ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'making-commerce-easy', '', '', '2014-03-03 12:42:30', '2014-03-03 17:42:30', '', 0, 'http://waq2014.lvh.me/?post_type=session&#038;p=760', 0, 'session', '', 0),
