(1067, 1, '2014-01-22 14:15:59', '2014-01-22 19:15:59', 'Dan Gill leads Leap Motion''s platform efforts for commercial applications, including working with large enterprise customers and the technology providers that serve them.  Dan has almost 20 years of experience leading sales and business development efforts for technology providers. Most recently he lead sales for several venture-backed companies (Bloomspot, BuyWithMe, Gotuit Media &amp; m-Qube) resulting in successful acquisitions by J.P. Morgan Chase, Gilt Groupe, Digitalsmiths and Verisign respectively. He earned a BA from Williams College and is a volunteer and fundraiser for Big Brothers Big Sisters.', 'Dan Gill', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '928-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-01-22 14:15:59', '2014-01-22 19:15:59', '', 928, 'http://waq2014.lvh.me/2014/01/22/928-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
